Brian Yun SUNG, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-0028 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. March 01, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Appellant's notice of voluntary dismissal is denied without prejudice to file an unconditional notice of voluntary dismissal. See Hammerl v. State, 779 So.2d 410 (Fla. 2d DCA 2000).
